summary: A spell that swap your clothes with someone else.
descriptionHtml:
Ok, I had a lot of stuff to do and suddenly some strange idea came to me, I play as a mage and always did so I create a couple spells sometime, simple spells to make Skyrim more funny, and this one I made today and he does exactly what is in the title, he swaps your clothes with someone else.
NOTE: Some clothes in the game (I don't know for sure if it's cuz other mods are running too) may not appear immediately on you, or you'll get bald or your head simple disappear, but relax, just put a ring or a necklace and you're fine again. Initial Release.

~REQUIRES SKSE~
The Spellbook can be found on the Arch-mage's Quarter, on the Arcane Enchanter :)
Anything, yell, or contact me via email, pm.. leave a comment below... up to you
author: Kernnunnos
